here's our host
Alyson Hannigan.

00:29.062 --> 00:32.032
[cheers and applause]

00:32.065 --> 00:39.105
♪ ♪

00:41.141 --> 00:42.709
- Welcome to "Fool Us."

00:42.742 --> 00:45.912
Tonight, we have
an abundance of baffling,

00:45.945 --> 00:49.215
a plethora of perplexing,
a myriad of magic,

00:49.249 --> 00:52.218
and clearly
a thesaurus backstage.

00:52.252 --> 00:55.688
We also have two
walking encyclopedias of magic,

00:55.722 --> 00:58.591
