neither of us see the card.

03:30.743 --> 03:31.978
- Okay.
- Just the guys.

03:32.011 --> 03:33.346
And then you're gonna
put it right back

03:33.379 --> 03:34.881
onto the deck of cards.
Does that make sense?

03:34.914 --> 03:36.349
- Yes.

03:36.382 --> 03:37.383
- Go ahead and pick up
a chunk of cards.

03:37.417 --> 03:39.185
Pick up a chunk of cards.
Show it to the guys.

03:39.219 --> 03:40.920
Guys, please remember
that bottom card.

03:40.954 --> 03:42.855
You guys got it?
All right.

03:42.889 --> 03:44.724
And put it back
onto the deck of cards.

03:44.757 --> 03:47.360
Now, Alyson,
I'm gonna find your card

03:47.393 --> 03:50.396
in the most dangerous way
possible...

03:50.430 --> 03:51.431
by stabbing to it.

03:51.464 --> 03:54.267
[laughter]

03:54.300 --> 03:57.070
One, two.

03:57.103 --> 03:59.005
Here's the thing.
[laughter]

03:59.038 --> 04:00.740
If I were to stab
to their card right now,

04:00.773 --> 04:04.644
that would be impressive,
but I'm a magician.

04:04.677 --> 04:09.782
However, you don't know
what their card is either.

04:09.816 --> 04:13.119
And if I mix these cards up,
Alyson,

04:13.152 --> 04:17.457
you wouldn't even know
the location of their card.

04:17.490 --> 04:19.325
Is that right?

04:19.359 --> 04:23.229
Which is why
I think you should do it.

04:23.263 --> 04:25.331
[laughter]

04:25.365 --> 04:27.133
- Stab the card?

04:27.166 --> 04:29.636
- One question. Are you
comfortable with a knife?

04:29.669 --> 04:33.039
- I mean, as long as it's not
near any body parts.

04:33.072 --> 04:35.475
- Oh, no.
- Then pick a knife.

04:35.508 --> 04:37.343
Any knife.
- Oh, dear.

04:37.377 --> 04:41.014
W-where is security?
[laughter]

04:41.047 --> 04:42.548
Uh.

04:42.582 --> 04:45.718
Pick a knife, any knife?
- Pick a knife, any knife.

04:45.752 --> 04:48.855
- Um, I'll do that one.

04:48.888 --> 04:50.356
- Go ahead and take it.
It's yours.

04:50.390 --> 04:51.658
Oh, this is weird.

04:51.691 --> 04:53.226
- By the way.
That's a really good choice.

04:53.259 --> 04:55.094
Now, Alyson, in a moment,

04:55.128 --> 04:58.064
