05:07.240 --> 05:08.975
- Okay.
- Okay.

05:09.008 --> 05:10.276
Hold the thumb on the top.

05:10.310 --> 05:11.944
- Okay. All right.
- Just like that.

05:11.978 --> 05:13.479
You don't hurt yourself
and we're gonna practice

05:13.513 --> 05:18.017
